casebody.data:
No. 10-751. Omar Khadr, et al., Petitioners v. Barack H. Obama, President of the United States, et al. 563 U.S. 1016, 131 S. Ct. 2900,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1262,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3936. May 23, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

Justice Breyer and Justice Soto-mayor would grant the petition for a writ of certiorari. Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
